==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Post note
<hw>Post" note`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Com.)</fld> <def>A note issued
by a bank, payable at some future specified time, as distinguished from
a note payable on demand.</def> <rj><au>Burrill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Postnuptial</ent>⟦br⟧
